Objective: Achieve >65% t + 1 directional accuracy on IDX short-term small/mid-cap setups using volume anomalies and social sentiment bursts.

KR1: Keep scraper runtime block rate below 5% through proxy rotation and randomized user agents.
KR2: Reduce IndoBERT slang sentiment classification error on short-horizon social samples below 15%.
KR3: Maintain rolling-window XGBoost precision >= 0.62 for 5m/15m interval experiments.
KR4: Keep execution risk engine false-trigger rate below 10% on replayed order-book sessions.
